<TEXT>
<P>
I read with interest Peter Steinhart's column ("Giving Our Children a Break," 
Opinion, Oct. 14) advocating passage of Prop. 128, Big Green. 
</P>
<P>
I was an early supporter and financial backer of Big Green. As I considered the 
