and a touchdown in 16 carries to lead the Saints to a Central League victory at 
Locke. Redmond missed two games this season with a hip injury. 
</P>
<P>
Courtney Bell added 68 yards in 14 carries in helping Locke compile 220 yards 
rushing. 
</P>
<P>
