<P>
PRODUCT RECALLS; DEFECTIVE PRODUCTS; DIVING 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102090-0114 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 295322 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 20, 1990, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
