room as her mother, Andi, ties her shoe. Furnishings are from the Bellini store 
in Costa Mesa. ; Photo, COLOR, Ashten Waks and Alex Wolfe, 2 1/2, jump on the 
Bellini bed in her room. The Bellini store specializes in beechwood furniture 
for children. ; Photo, Above: Jim and Linda Andrews with their 6 1/2-month-old 
daughter, Christina, in her newly decorated nursery. Below: Interior designer 
Elaine Hankin in front of a mural she selected for Christina's room. LACY 
ATKINS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
