Judge Lets P.I.E. Use Cash: A federal bankruptcy judge in Jacksonville, Fla., 
said Olympia Holdings Inc. could use $24.4 million in cash from accounts 
receivable to fund its P.I.E. International trucking unit. The cash infusion 
won't prevent cutbacks at the unit, which plans to lay off 20% of its 7,500 
